snippet: Hannah Kearney of the United States, the Olympic and World Cup champion, won the women’s gold medal in moguls at the freestyle skiing world championships in Voss, Norway.
lead_paragraph: Hannah Kearney of the United States, the Olympic and World Cup champion, won the women’s gold medal in moguls at the freestyle skiing world championships in Voss, Norway.

headline.seo: American Takes Gold at Freestyle Skiing Worlds
headline.main: American Takes Gold at Freestyle Skiing Worlds
